    "attributes": {
        "action": "Pay 15% bonus to public facing NHS staff",
        "additional_details": "NHS staff have been fighting a deadly battle where their dedication to duty and service has been nothing less than heroic. A pay bonus will enable them to hopefully take a deserved holiday and rest with their families. It would also be a meaningful way to express the thanks of the nation for the care and support the NHS have provided.",
        "background": "The covid pandemic has required NHS public facing staff to put themselves in harms way to treat and care for covid patients. and their families.",
